SELECT DISTINCT p.paper_id,
       p.title,
       p.abstract,
       p.venue,
       p.year,
       p.citation_count,
       p.open_access_url
FROM Papers p
LEFT JOIN PaperAuthors pa ON p.paper_id = pa.paper_id
LEFT JOIN Authors a ON pa.author_id = a.author_id
WHERE (p.title ILIKE '%smartphone%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%smartphone%')
  AND (p.title ILIKE '%honary%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%honary%' OR a.name ILIKE '%honary%')
  AND (p.title ILIKE '%computer science%' OR p.abstract ILIKE '%computer science%' OR p.venue ILIKE '%computer science%')
